### Youyu - Orders
### Prerequisite: backend started with -Dspring-boot.run.profiles=seed
### Cart and payment examples live in cart.http and payment.http.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@buyerToken = mock-1001-USER
@otherUserToken = mock-1004-USER
@adminToken = mock-9001-ADMIN
@seedDetailOrderId = 8812
@seedRefundOrderId = 8808
@seedRefundId = 1

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Buyer orders
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

### List own orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

###

### Preview order from selected cart items
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartItemIds": [1],
  "fulfillmentType": "logistics"
}

###

### Preview order with a claimed coupon
### Replace userCouponId with a value returned by POST /api/marketing/coupons/{couponId}/claim.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartItemIds": [1],
  "fulfillmentType": "logistics",
  "userCouponId": 1
}

###

### Create logistics order from selected cart items
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartItemIds": [1],
  "fulfillmentType": "logistics",
  "addressId": 1,
  "buyerNote": "Please deliver to the campus gate."
}

###

### Create order with a claimed coupon; server revalidates coupon eligibility
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartItemIds": [1],
  "fulfillmentType": "logistics",
  "addressId": 1,
  "userCouponId": 1,
  "buyerNote": "Use one approved shop coupon."
}

###

### Create offline order from selected cart items
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cartItemIds": [1],
  "fulfillmentType": "offline",
  "offlineMeetTime": "2026-05-27 14:30",
  "offlineMeetLocation": "Library entrance",
  "buyerNote": "I will arrive after class."
}

###

### Get order detail
### Expected detail now includes refundRuleText, relatedReports, mediationSummary,
### afterSalesSummary, and for logistics orders logisticsTracking/logisticsMap.
### With default local config, logisticsTracking.status is "disabled" and
### logisticsMap.status is "map_provider_disabled"; no provider network call is made.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{seedDetailOrderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

###

### Get another user's order detail - expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{seedDetailOrderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### Cancel order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/8821/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

###

### Confirm receipt (logistics or digital)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/8823/confirm-receipt
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

###

### Buyer confirm offline delivery
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/8815/offline/buyer-confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

###

### Request refund
### Uses a seeded paid logistics order with persisted payment_records + order_fulfillments.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{seedRefundOrderId}}/refunds
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refundReason": "Product does not match the listing."
}

###

### Duplicate refund for order already refunding - expect BUSINESS_ERROR
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{seedRefundOrderId}}/refunds
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refundReason": "Second refund request should be rejected."
}

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Admin order view
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

###

### Admin list all orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Admin get order detail
### Expected detail now includes the same after-sales visibility family, with admin seeing all relatedReports for the order.
### Logistics orders include logisticsTracking/logisticsMap payloads without requiring real provider credentials.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/{{seedDetailOrderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Admin ship logistics order
### Precondition: use a logistics order that has already been paid and is still pending fulfillment.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/8001/ship
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNo": "SF1234567890",
  "logisticsCompany": "SF Express"
}

###

### Admin confirm offline seller delivery
### Precondition: use an offline order that has already been paid and is waiting for seller-side confirmation.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/8003/offline/seller-confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Admin complete refund
### Run after the refund request above and replace seedRefundId when a different refund record is created.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/{{seedRefundOrderId}}/refunds/{{seedRefundId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Repeat admin refund completion - expect the same completed detail
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/{{seedRefundOrderId}}/refunds/{{seedRefundId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Digital asset access
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

###

### Access full digital asset (requires confirmed receipt)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/8813/assets/3203/access
Authorization: Bearer {{buyerToken}}

###

### Access full asset without receipt - expect BUSINESS_ERROR
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/8823/assets/3203/access
Authorization: Bearer mock-1002-USER

###

### Non-buyer cannot access full asset - expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/8813/assets/3203/access
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}
